"\n"
"• Descendants — shows all descendants in a Henry-numbered report.\n"
"\n"
"Names in both reports are clickable links to that person's Bio."
msgstr ""
"Wenn der Modus Profil aktiv ist, können Sie zwischen drei Ansichten wechseln:\n"
